title: List of characters created for Game of Thrones
summary: This page lists the characters that have been created for Game of Thrones, the television adaptation of the A Song of Ice and Fire novels, and have no equivalent counterpart in the books. The characters are listed according to their first appearance or mention in the series.
content:
